{"tid":555381,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"用緊iphone嘅耳機神請入","createTime":"2018-02-09T11:30:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T12:11:38.000Z","uid":141934,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5e7f218e715b810ba98df19fc1f0e6547d0463b7","tid":555381,"uid":141934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T11:30:47.000Z","msg":"小弟一直用ipse 前排部機跌爆左唸住轉機，新出嘅ip8 同ipx都冇3.5頭 要加adapter，聽人講條線會降低耳機音質，應該如何解決問題，買android機好定點,想知條線差幾多，如果android機，mate10 pro 好唔好.小弟耳機ue900s，"},{"pid":"09c73a79849b26c48afd7275116616740d36a107","tid":555381,"uid":83712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T12:51:55.000Z","msg":"可以買有dac耳擴嘅adapter<br />\nandroid 嘅話聽講LG V30同dp-cmx1都好聲<br />\n再唔係買player一定好聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c2060b4af48b5c22006e6e014c53349f9bc59c","tid":555381,"uid":37820,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T12:58:28.000Z","msg":"Iphone聽就是但 一係買個support lightning嘅fac<br />\nAndroid 電話就onkyo cmx1<br />\n華為啲電子垃圾就唔好提啦"},{"pid":"8f2b87afadadab96575b343b0340dc7a5d97f62f","tid":555381,"uid":82970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T02:51:47.000Z","msg":"果個唔係完全adapter，入面有張DAC，算係外置DAC，唔關手機連去DAC條線事，入面行數碼信號。Lightning同USB Type-C一樣原理，手機內置冇DAC，轉用外置DAC，重點係睇粒DAC質素，不過另外買DAC真係好反智，負皮依個設計，逼人用藍牙耳機。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"122a06c7c942c4668ca10678cbd923f5f5ced4ff","tid":555381,"uid":147057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T12:11:38.000Z","msg":"本身iPhone又唔係特別好聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多條老鼠尾同冇 我覺得差唔多<br />\n想換Android要好聲 首選CMX1<br />\n基本上係附送打電話功能既DAP<br />\n似返部電話既咪揀V30咯<br />\n<br />\n華為？不予置評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}